{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/life-events/birthdays-and-anniversaries","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Birthdays and anniversaries ","meta_description":"Celebrations of birthdays or anniversaries can only be carried out among your closest family and loved ones (in particular your partner).","content":{"processed":"<h2>Pravidla a doporučení</h2>\n<p>Oslava narozenin nebo jiných výročí se nyní může <strong>konat jen v rámci nejužší rodiny a osob blízkých</strong> (to je zejména přítel nebo přítelkyně). <strong>Oslavu s kamarády nebo širší rodinou </strong>(např. sestřenice, bratranec, teta, strýc apod.) <strong>odložte na později. </strong></p>\n<p>Pokud již oslavu narozenin v rámci nejužšího okruhu rodiny organizujete, <strong>zvažte přítomnost rizikových skupin</strong>, zejména prarodičů. Dodržujte hygienická opatření, např. <strong>pravidelné větrání místnosti</strong>, aby zde proudil čerstvý vzduch, <strong>nepřekřikujte se</strong>, neboť tím dochází k vyššímu šíření kapének. <strong>Pokud se chcete chovat preventivně</strong>, můžete mít během oslavy roušku, před přáním oslavenci si vydezinfikovat ruce nebo sedět s většími rozestupy. Ruce si umyjte i před jídlem.</p>\n<p><strong>Oslavu není možné mít v baru, klubu, restauraci, cukrárně, kavárně</strong> ani jiném podobném zařízení. Ta jsou nyní pro veřejnost zavřená.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/birthdays-and-anniversaries"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-05T20:53:29+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"contact_page"},"situation_type":{"name":"Life events","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"supervisor_account"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Mode of operation","path":{"alias":"/situations/restaurants/mode-operation","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Indoor","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks/indoor","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Retail","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/retail","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Children's contact with their friends","path":{"alias":"/situations/parents/childrens-contact-their-friends","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Keeping in touch with family","path":{"alias":"/situations/seniors/keeping-touch-family","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-11-05T21:53:29+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Life events","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"supervisor_account"},"situation":[{"id":"f165596a-d1b6-5819-9518-2ed5402a4082","title":"Pregnancy and childbirth","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/pregnancy-and-childbirth"}},{"id":"7994815d-2868-5525-82c7-fd9202082dfc","title":"Weddings ","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/weddings"}},{"id":"21020032-50f2-58f3-bd5d-c331221143a0","title":"Birthdays and anniversaries ","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/birthdays-and-anniversaries"}},{"id":"8ba3156d-9274-5a6f-bd62-98804138f96e","title":"Funerals","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/funerals"}},{"id":"88219d06-7a83-5a17-ae43-77b6a776e27b","title":"Buying real estate and moving in or out","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/buying-real-estate-and-moving-or-out"}},{"id":"4d75d471-db8e-5f84-9777-055dd43780a9","title":"Graduation","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/graduation"}},{"id":"a7da4326-fa30-5f9b-b0a3-2c862e83a471","title":"Registered partnership","path":{"alias":"/situations/life-events/registered-partnership"}}]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/situations/life-events/birthdays-and-anniversaries","langCode":"en","listSlug":"/situations/life-events","languageVariants":{"cs":"/situace/zivotni-udalosti/narozeniny-vyroci"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["106679691","1119304123","1211267612","1211267612","2446164016","4279535114"]}